1. Can i change type of the Ec2 instance after Launch the EC2.?

Ans: Yes we can Change the type of the Ec2 instance after Launch
		--> Stop the Ec2 instance --> Actions --> instance settings
		--> change instance type --> select the new type of the instace whichever you want..
		
	Read official Document: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/ec2-instance-resize.html
